301
00:14:28,740 --> 00:14:29,880
(Blown-tire bus overturned
on Hua'an Road in Shi'an Town, 1 dead)

302
00:14:29,880 --> 00:14:31,231
Officer Deng, it's him.

303
00:14:33,231 --> 00:14:34,871
