306
00:14:50,471 --> 00:14:52,231
Quanquan.

307
00:14:53,392 --> 00:14:54,471
Don't be upset.

308
00:14:54,471 --> 00:14:56,312
Mommy has something important to handle.

309
00:14:56,312 --> 00:14:56,951
Why?

310
00:14:56,951 --> 00:14:58,672
