340
00:16:13,831 --> 00:16:14,871
What's in there?

341
00:16:14,871 --> 00:16:16,231
Our dinner.

342
00:16:16,351 --> 00:16:17,072
Come on. Let's go.

343
00:16:17,072 --> 00:16:18,312
