344
00:16:20,111 --> 00:16:20,912
Hello, Mr. Zhou.

345
00:16:21,152 --> 00:16:21,831
Hello.

346
00:16:21,831 --> 00:16:24,591
Steak, mushroom, and pear.

347
00:16:24,672 --> 00:16:26,272
