514
00:23:34,712 --> 00:23:35,831
Open the door.

515
00:23:41,552 --> 00:23:42,671
Open the door.

516
00:23:42,952 --> 00:23:43,792
Move to the side.

517
00:23:43,792 --> 00:23:45,072
This side.

518
00:23:47,552 --> 00:23:49,272
Here. Faster.

519
00:23:51,232 --> 00:23:54,032
Give me your hand.

520
00:23:57,351 --> 00:23:58,552
Don't move.

521
